This paper is about building artificial intelligence systems that can reason and answer questions about visual data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories of arXiv CS.
